title.rendered: HSP Taillock Tailgate Central Locking (With Plug And Play Wiring) – Mitsubishi Triton MQ 2015 – 10/2018 & Mitsubishi Triton 11/2018 +

content.rendered:
HSP Taillock Tailgate Central Locking (With Plug And Play Wiring) – Mitsubishi Triton MQ 2015 – 10/2018 & Mitsubishi Triton 11/2018 +  (Suits premium models with larger tailgate handle)

 

 

– Powder Coated steel frame
– Spring-loaded latch pins allow you to
position the tray into multiple positions
–  75% extension
– 250 kgs loading capacity  (dispersed weight extended)
– Compatible with most bed/tub liners
– Precision cut platform
